If you continue ignoring my attacks, Jason, I'm gonna get really mad. So post 
damage.

::DevilDuer/Oblitertron::

Two of Oblitertron's giant fingers close in on Squizzy, grabbing her and 
giving a strong pull away from Arcangel. With any luck, he'd get her out of 
Arcangel's grip, Oblitertron was very strong.

As he tugged, Oblitertron shoots his optics again at Arcangel.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
DevilDuer, leaking fluid from the shoulder, curses as Oblitertron's hand 
blocks his line of fire, moving to get a shot. He aims carefully, firing his 
stun gun at Arcangel.
